{"data":{"id":6,"created_at":"2026-04-21T06:51:00.193476Z","updated_at":"2026-04-21T07:55:12.023479Z","name":"ZPass – Welcome aboard","subject":"You're on the ZPass list","type":"tx","body":"\u003c!--\r\n  ZPass — 订阅成功欢迎邮件 (Transactional · 双语)\r\n  SUBJECT: 由 /api/tx 的 `subject` 字段按语言动态传入\r\n          - en: You're on the ZPass list\r\n          - zh: 已加入 ZPass 候补名单\r\n  变量:\r\n    - {{ .Subscriber.Email }}     订阅者邮箱（/api/tx 的 subscriber_emails 自动绑定）\r\n    - {{ .Tx.Data.unsub_url }}    退订链接（可选）\r\n    - {{ .Tx.Data.lang }}         \"zh\" | \"en\"（默认 en）\r\n  备注:\r\n    listmonk v5 Transactional 模板上下文只有 { Subscriber, Tx }，没有原生 .UnsubURL，\r\n    所以通过 .Tx.Data.* 由外部显式传入。\r\n  用途: 用户点击 double-opt-in 确认链接后发送（需外部触发 /api/tx）\r\n--\u003e\r\n{{ $zh := eq .Tx.Data.lang \"zh\" -}}\r\n\u003c!doctype html\u003e\r\n\u003chtml lang=\"{{ if $zh }}zh-CN{{ else }}en{{ end }}\"\u003e\r\n  \u003chead\u003e\r\n    \u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003cmeta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003cmeta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"dark\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003cmeta name=\"supported-color-schemes\" content=\"dark\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003ctitle\u003e{{ if $zh }}已加入 ZPass 候补名单{{ else }}You're on the ZPass list{{ end }}\u003c/title\u003e\r\n    \u003cstyle\u003e\r\n      :root { color-scheme: dark; }\r\n      body { margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; background: #0c0c0d !important; }\r\n      a { text-decoration: none; }\r\n      @media (max-width: 620px) {\r\n        .zp-shell { width: 100% !important; padding: 24px 16px !important; }\r\n        .zp-card  { padding: 28px 20px !important; border-radius: 10px !important; }\r\n        .zp-h1    { font-size: 22px !important; line-height: 1.3 !important; }\r\n        .zp-step  { display: block !important; padding: 14px 16px !important; }\r\n        .zp-step-num { margin-bottom: 6px !important; }\r\n      }\r\n      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\r\n        .zp-bg   { background: #0c0c0d !important; }\r\n        .zp-card { background: #111113 !important; }\r\n        .zp-step-row { background: #16161a !important; }\r\n        .zp-text { color: #ececec !important; }\r\n        .zp-mute { color: #a8a8ac !important; }\r\n      }\r\n    \u003c/style\u003e\r\n  \u003c/head\u003e\r\n  \u003cbody\r\n    class=\"zp-bg\"\r\n    style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#0c0c0d;font-family:'Geist',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,'Helvetica Neue','PingFang SC','Hiragino Sans GB','Microsoft YaHei',Arial,sans-serif;color:#ececec;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"\r\n  \u003e\r\n    \u003c!-- 预览文字 --\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\r\n      style=\"display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;mso-hide:all;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;color:#0c0c0d;opacity:0;\"\r\n    \u003e\r\n      {{ if $zh }}你已确认订阅。ZPass 发布时我们会第一时间告知你——除此之外不会发任何邮件。{{ else }}You're confirmed. We'll email you the moment ZPass ships — and nothing else.{{ end }}\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003ctable\r\n      role=\"presentation\"\r\n      width=\"100%\"\r\n      cellpadding=\"0\"\r\n      cellspacing=\"0\"\r\n      border=\"0\"\r\n      style=\"background:#0c0c0d;\"\r\n    \u003e\r\n      \u003ctr\u003e\r\n        \u003ctd align=\"center\" style=\"padding:48px 16px;\"\u003e\r\n          \u003ctable\r\n            role=\"presentation\"\r\n            class=\"zp-shell\"\r\n            width=\"600\"\r\n            cellpadding=\"0\"\r\n            cellspacing=\"0\"\r\n            border=\"0\"\r\n            style=\"width:600px;max-width:600px;\"\r\n          \u003e\r\n            \u003c!-- ===== 品牌头 ===== --\u003e\r\n            \u003ctr\u003e\r\n              \u003ctd style=\"padding:0 4px 20px 4px;\"\u003e\r\n                \u003ctable role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\"\u003e\r\n                  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd align=\"left\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"\u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan\r\n                        style=\"display:inline-block;width:22px;height:22px;background:#d4ff3a;border-radius:5px;vertical-align:middle;\"\r\n                      \u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan\r\n                        style=\"display:inline-block;margin-left:10px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#ececec;vertical-align:middle;\"\r\n                        class=\"zp-text\"\r\n                        \u003eZPass\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      align=\"right\"\r\n                      style=\"vertical-align:middle;font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#6e6e73;text-transform:uppercase;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      {{ if $zh }}已确认{{ else }}CONFIRMED{{ end }}\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/table\u003e\r\n              \u003c/td\u003e\r\n            \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n\r\n            \u003c!-- ===== 主卡片 ===== --\u003e\r\n            \u003ctr\u003e\r\n              \u003ctd\r\n                class=\"zp-card\"\r\n                style=\"background:#111113;border:1px solid #232328;border-radius:10px;padding:40px 40px 36px 40px;\"\r\n              \u003e\r\n                \u003c!-- 成功徽章 --\u003e\r\n                \u003ctable role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 22px 0;\"\u003e\r\n                  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      style=\"background:rgba(212,255,58,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(212,255,58,0.2);border-radius:999px;padding:6px 12px;font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#d4ff3a;text-transform:uppercase;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      ✓ \u0026nbsp;{{ if $zh }}已成功加入{{ else }}You're in{{ end }}\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/table\u003e\r\n\r\n                \u003c!-- 标题 --\u003e\r\n                \u003ch1\r\n                  class=\"zp-h1 zp-text\"\r\n                  style=\"margin:0 0 14px 0;font-family:'Geist',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,'PingFang SC','Hiragino Sans GB','Microsoft YaHei',sans-serif;font-size:26px;line-height:1.25;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#ececec;\"\r\n                \u003e\r\n                  {{ if $zh }}感谢确认——ZPass 发布时我们会第一时间告知你。{{ else }}Thanks for confirming — you'll hear from us when ZPass ships.{{ end }}\r\n                \u003c/h1\u003e\r\n\r\n                \u003c!-- 正文 --\u003e\r\n                \u003cp\r\n                  class=\"zp-mute\"\r\n                  style=\"margin:0 0 28px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#a8a8ac;\"\r\n                \u003e\r\n                  {{ if $zh -}}\r\n                  \u003cspan style=\"color:#ececec;font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"\u003e{{ .Subscriber.Email }}\u003c/span\u003e\r\n                  已加入 ZPass 抢先体验名单。你只会收到一封邮件——当 1.0 版本为你所用平台开放下载的那一天。之前、之后都不会再打扰你。\r\n                  {{- else -}}\r\n                  \u003cspan style=\"color:#ececec;font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"\u003e{{ .Subscriber.Email }}\u003c/span\u003e\r\n                  is now on the ZPass early-access list. You'll get exactly one email — the day version 1.0 is available for your platform. Nothing before, nothing after.\r\n                  {{- end }}\r\n                \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n                \u003c!-- 产品承诺列表 --\u003e\r\n                \u003ctable role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;\"\u003e\r\n                  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      class=\"zp-step-row zp-step\"\r\n                      style=\"background:#16161a;border:1px solid #232328;border-radius:7px;padding:14px 16px;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan\r\n                        class=\"zp-step-num\"\r\n                        style=\"display:inline-block;min-width:22px;font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:11px;color:#6e6e73;letter-spacing:0.04em;\"\r\n                        \u003e01\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan class=\"zp-text\" style=\"color:#ececec;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"\r\n                        \u003e{{ if $zh }}端到端加密。{{ else }}End-to-end encrypted.{{ end }}\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan class=\"zp-mute\" style=\"color:#a8a8ac;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"\u003e\r\n                        \u0026nbsp;{{ if $zh }}XChaCha20-Poly1305 + Argon2id。主密码从不离开你的设备。{{ else }}XChaCha20-Poly1305 + Argon2id. Your master password never leaves your device.{{ end }}\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/table\u003e\r\n                \u003ctable role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;\"\u003e\r\n                  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      class=\"zp-step-row zp-step\"\r\n                      style=\"background:#16161a;border:1px solid #232328;border-radius:7px;padding:14px 16px;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan\r\n                        class=\"zp-step-num\"\r\n                        style=\"display:inline-block;min-width:22px;font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:11px;color:#6e6e73;letter-spacing:0.04em;\"\r\n                        \u003e02\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan class=\"zp-text\" style=\"color:#ececec;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"\r\n                        \u003e{{ if $zh }}首发即支持全平台。{{ else }}Cross-platform from day one.{{ end }}\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan class=\"zp-mute\" style=\"color:#a8a8ac;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"\u003e\r\n                        \u0026nbsp;{{ if $zh }}macOS · Windows · Linux · iOS · Android · 浏览器扩展。{{ else }}macOS · Windows · Linux · iOS · Android · browser extensions.{{ end }}\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/table\u003e\r\n                \u003ctable role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 28px 0;\"\u003e\r\n                  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      class=\"zp-step-row zp-step\"\r\n                      style=\"background:#16161a;border:1px solid #232328;border-radius:7px;padding:14px 16px;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan\r\n                        class=\"zp-step-num\"\r\n                        style=\"display:inline-block;min-width:22px;font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:11px;color:#6e6e73;letter-spacing:0.04em;\"\r\n                        \u003e03\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan class=\"zp-text\" style=\"color:#ececec;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"\r\n                        \u003e{{ if $zh }}无营销，无追踪。{{ else }}No marketing, no tracking.{{ end }}\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                      \u003cspan class=\"zp-mute\" style=\"color:#a8a8ac;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"\u003e\r\n                        \u0026nbsp;{{ if $zh }}一键退订，始终如此。我们绝不分享你的地址。{{ else }}One-tap unsubscribe, always. We never share your address.{{ end }}\u003c/span\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/table\u003e\r\n\r\n                \u003c!-- 返回官网 CTA --\u003e\r\n                \u003ctable role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\"\u003e\r\n                  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      style=\"border:1px solid #232328;border-radius:7px;background:transparent;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      \u003ca\r\n                        href=\"{{ if $zh }}https://zpass.zerx.dev/zh/{{ else }}https://zpass.zerx.dev/{{ end }}\"\r\n                        target=\"_blank\"\r\n                        style=\"display:inline-block;padding:11px 22px;font-family:'Geist',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,'PingFang SC','Hiragino Sans GB','Microsoft YaHei',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#ececec;text-decoration:none;\"\r\n                        \u003e{{ if $zh }}了解更多 ZPass\u0026nbsp;→{{ else }}Read more about ZPass\u0026nbsp;→{{ end }}\u003c/a\r\n                      \u003e\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/table\u003e\r\n              \u003c/td\u003e\r\n            \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n\r\n            \u003c!-- ===== 页脚 ===== --\u003e\r\n            \u003ctr\u003e\r\n              \u003ctd style=\"padding:28px 4px 0 4px;\"\u003e\r\n                \u003ctable role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\"\u003e\r\n                  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      align=\"left\"\r\n                      style=\"font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.04em;color:#45454a;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      {{ if $zh }}© 2026 ZPass · 端到端加密的密码管理器{{ else }}© 2026 ZPass · End-to-end encrypted password manager{{ end }}\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                    \u003ctd\r\n                      align=\"right\"\r\n                      style=\"font-family:'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:11px;color:#45454a;\"\r\n                    \u003e\r\n                      {{ if .Tx.Data.unsub_url }}\u003ca href=\"{{ .Tx.Data.unsub_url }}\" style=\"color:#6e6e73;text-decoration:none;\"\u003e{{ if $zh }}退订{{ else }}Unsubscribe{{ end }}\u003c/a\u003e{{ end }}\r\n                    \u003c/td\u003e\r\n                  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/table\u003e\r\n              \u003c/td\u003e\r\n            \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003c/table\u003e\r\n        \u003c/td\u003e\r\n      \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n    \u003c/table\u003e\r\n  \u003c/body\u003e\r\n\u003c/html\u003e\r\n","body_source":null,"is_default":false}}
